OL,3,CPatients and staff led to safety after
OL,4,Chuge fire at hospital
OL,6,FPatients and staff have been led to
OL,7,Fsafety after a huge fire at a hospital
OL,8,Fin North Yorkshire.
OL,10,FThe blaze in a building at the Malton
OL,11,Fand Norton District Hospital site
OL,12,Fbroke out on Wednesday morning, 8 July.
OL,14,FSeveral crews from North Yorkshire
OL,15,FFire and Rescue Service are on the
OL,16,Fscene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
