OL,3,CPatients and staff led to safety after
OL,4,Chuge fire at hospital
OL,6,FIn a statement, York and Scarborough
OL,7,FTeaching Hospitals NHS Trust said:
OL,8,F"All patients and colleagues have been
OL,9,Fsafely evacuated, and there are no
OL,10,Freports of any injuries.
OL,12,F"Anyone with an appointment at Malton
OL,13,FHospital today should not attend.
OL,15,F"Our teams are reviewing all affected
OL,16,Fappointments and will contact patients
OL,17,Fdirectly as soon as possible to
OL,18,Frearrange or advise on the next steps."
OL,20,FMalton Urgent Treatment Centre was
OL,21,Falso closed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
