OL,3,CPatients and staff led to safety after
OL,4,Chuge fire at hospital
OL,6,FA fire service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Residents and anyone nearby may
OL,8,Fnotice large amounts of smoke. As a
OL,9,Fprecaution, please keep all doors and
OL,10,Fwindows closed.
OL,12,F"Please avoid the area at this time to
OL,13,Fallow emergency services access."
OL,15,FMore updates to follow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
